n# Task Manager App

![Task Manager Screenshot](./screenshots/app-preview.png)

A modern task management application built with React, Vite, and Tailwind CSS featuring dark/light mode, API integration, and responsive design.

## Features

- 📝 Task management (Create, Complete, Delete, Filter)
- 🌓 Light/Dark mode toggle
- 🔍 API data fetching with search and pagination
- 📱 Fully responsive design
- 🚀 Optimized with Vite
- 🎨 Styled with Tailwind CSS
- 🔄 State persistence using localStorage

## Technologies

- ⚛️ React 18
- ⚡ Vite
- 🎨 Tailwind CSS
- 🔀 React Router
- 📦 React Icons (optional)

